# API Contract — DEPRECATED (no API server)

This rule file is kept as a tombstone. There is no custom HTTP API in Kupay as of 2026-05-19.

Mobile/web talk to Supabase directly. The "contract" between client and DB is:
- Postgres schema + RLS in `cost-share-app/supabase/schema.sql`.
- Row mappers and domain types in `packages/shared/src/{mappers,types}/`.

See `docs/SSOT/CODE QUALITY.md` for the current architecture.
